subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: The South Korean rookie Sei Young Kim won the Bahamas L.P.G.A. Classic for her first L.P.G.A. Tour title, sinking an 8-foot birdie putt on the first hole of a playoff with her countrywoman Sun Young Yoo and Ariya Jutanugarn of Thailand.
